name: Snowies Brumby Under the Trees
description:
This magnificent brumby stallion was relaxed but alert when he was originally photographed under the trees in Australia's beautiful Snowy Mountains. He was not yet old enough to have a herd of his own so was by himself. 

I used ArtRage to create this textured image in 2019, and am now grateful to be able to share my art with a wider audience.
